   <body>
      <table colsep="1" rowsep="1">
         <desc>
            <p>The following table provides the workflow actions and status (current and
subsequent status) of the <uicontrol>Planned
Project</uicontrol> record.</p>
            <p>For information on setting a workflow status to the next status, refer to <xref href="../../../Common_Application_Features/Workflow_Management/WFStgTrans.xml"/>.</p>
         </desc>
         <tgroup cols="6">
            <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1"/>
            <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2"/>
            <colspec colname="c3" colnum="3"/>
            <colspec colname="c4" colnum="4"/>
            <colspec colname="c5" colnum="5"/>
            <colspec colname="c6" colnum="6"/>
            <thead>
               <row>
                  <entry>Phase</entry>
                  <entry>Current Workflow Status</entry>
                  <entry>Action Stakeholders</entry>
                  <entry>Action </entry>
                  <entry>Subsequent Workflow Status</entry>
                  <entry>Comments</entry>
               </row>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
               <row>
                  <entry morerows="1">1</entry>
                  <entry morerows="1"> Draft </entry>
                  <entry morerows="1">
                     <ul>
                        <li>Director</li>
                        <li>Fund Manager</li>
                        <li>Manager</li>
                        <li>Project Manager</li>
                        <li>Support Services</li>
                     </ul>
                  </entry>
                  <entry>Publish</entry>
                  <entry>Published</entry>
                  <entry>
                     <p>Only funded projects associated with either  <uicontrol>Stormwater Administration</uicontrol> or <uicontrol>Engineering and Capital Improvements Administration</uicontrol> as the Owning Department can Publish a project. </p>
                     <p>You can now add this planned project to a program. The project is approved when the program is approved. </p>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry>Approve</entry>
                  <entry>Pre-Award</entry>
                  <entry>
                     <ul>
                        <li>Unfunded &amp; Standalone projects associated with any Owning Department can be approved. These projects do not require any program approval.</li>
                        <li>Standalone projects that will receive funding and are associated with any Owning Department, except <uicontrol>Stormwater Administration</uicontrol> or <uicontrol>Engineering and Capital Improvements Administration </uicontrol>, can be approved. These projects do not require any program approval. </li>
                     </ul>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry morerows="2">2</entry>
                  <entry morerows="2">Published</entry>
                  <entry morerows="2">
                     <ul>
                        <li>Fund Manager</li>
                        <li>Support Services</li>
                     </ul>
                  </entry>
                  <entry morerows="1">Approve</entry>
                  <entry>Planned</entry>
                  <entry>If the funded project is Out-Year, the status is updated to Planned.</entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry>Pre-Award</entry>
                  <entry>
                            If the funded project is In-Year, the status is updated to Pre-Award.</entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry>Un-Publish</entry>
                  <entry>Draft</entry>
                  <entry>-</entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry morerows="1">3</entry>
                  <entry morerows="1">Planned</entry>
                  <entry morerows="1">
                     <ul>
                        <li>Fund Manager</li>
                        <li>Support Services</li>
                     </ul>
                  </entry>
                  <entry>Pre-Award</entry>
                  <entry>Pre-Award</entry>
                  <entry>This workflow action is available only if the start date of the funded project is not in the current
fiscal year.<p>The project is now available in the<uicontrol>Projects</uicontrol>module and not in the<uicontrol>Planning</uicontrol>module.</p>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry>Re-Draft</entry>
                  <entry>Draft</entry>
                  <entry>If the  funded project associated with either <uicontrol>Stormwater Administration</uicontrol> or <uicontrol>Engineering and Capital Improvements Administration </uicontrol> is already associated with a program, this workflow action will be available. </entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry morerows="1">4</entry>
                  <entry morerows="1">Pre-Award</entry>
                  <entry morerows="1">
                     <ul>
                        <li>Fund Manager</li>
                        <li>Manager</li>
                        <li>Project Manager</li>
                        <li>Support Services</li>
                     </ul>
                  </entry>
                  <entry>Execute</entry>
                  <entry>In Progress</entry>
                  <entry>-</entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry>Re-Draft</entry>
                  <entry>Draft</entry>
                  <entry>This workflow action can be completed only for unfunded or standalone projects.</entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry>5</entry>
                  <entry>In Progress</entry>
                  <entry>
                     <ul>
                        <li>Fund Manager</li>
                        <li>Project Manager</li>
                        <li>Support Services</li>
                     </ul>
                  </entry>
                  <entry>Close </entry>
                  <entry>Closed</entry>
                  <entry morerows="1">This workflow action can be completed for funded, unfunded, and standalone projects. </entry>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <entry>6</entry>
                  <entry>Closed</entry>
                  <entry>
                     <ul>
                        <li>Fund Manager</li>
                        <li>Manager</li>
                        <li>Project Manager</li>
                        <li>Support Services</li>
                     </ul>
                  </entry>
                  <entry>Final Close</entry>
                  <entry>Final Closed</entry>
               </row>
            </tbody>
         </tgroup>
      </table>
